        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1302667634" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13613523345444038541">Eckhart Tolle is an excellent teacher. He teaches us a simple concept of living in the now and what happiness and blessings can be gleened from this practice. <br/>It is a very strait forward teaching but with Tolle&apos;s dynamic writing style he brings each page to life for the reader.<br/>I recommend this book to all.<br/>Yesterday is history;<br/>Tomorrow is a mystry;<br/>Today is a gift from God.<br/>That&apos;s why we call it the present.<br/>Enjoy and Be Blessed.<br/>Diamond</span>
  <span id="freeText13613523345444038541" style="display:none">Eckhart Tolle is an excellent teacher. He teaches us a simple concept of living in the now and what happiness and blessings can be gleened from this practice. <br />It is a very strait forward teaching but with Tolle's dynamic writing style he brings each page to life for the reader.<br />I recommend this book to all.<br />Yesterday is history;<br />Tomorrow is a mystry;<br />Today is a gift from God.<br />That's why we call it the present.<br />Enjoy and Be Blessed.<br />Diamond</span>
