<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2253441338230766534">Eckhart Tolle is a teacher, author, and entrepreneur. He is a German-born resident of Canada best known as the author of <em>The Power of Now</em> and <em>A New Earth: Awakening to Your Life&apos;s Purpose</em>. Tolle does not identify with any specific religion, but he has been influenced by multiple spiritual works.</span>
  <span id="freeText2253441338230766534" style="display:none">Eckhart Tolle is a teacher, author, and entrepreneur. He is a German-born resident of Canada best known as the author of <em>The Power of Now</em> and <em>A New Earth: Awakening to Your Life's Purpose</em>. Tolle does not identify with any specific religion, but he has been influenced by multiple spiritual works.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2253441338230766534" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

